 10 temporary HP, attack modifier +18, damage bonus +8, and Acrobatics +20.DESC:&nl;Heightened (6th) Your battle form is Huge, your fly Speed gains a +15-foot status bonus, and your attacks have 10-foot reach. You must have enough space to expand into or the spell is lost. You instead gain AC = 21 + your level, 15 temporary HP, attack modifier +21, damage bonus +4 and double damage dice (including persistent damage), and Acrobatics +23.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														INFO:SpellLevel|4	INFO:Casting|somatic, verbal
