e 3d10 bludgeoning;  horns (reach 10 feet), Damage 3d8 piercing; breath weapon 60-foot line, 11d6 acid. * Blue burrow Speed 20 feet;  jaws, Damage 2d10 piercing plus 1d12 electricity;  claw (agile), Damage 3d10 slashing;  tail (reach 10 feet), Damage 3d10 bludgeoning;  horns (reach 10 feet), Damage 3d8 piercing; breath weapon 80-foot line, 6d12 electricity. * Green swim Speed 40 feet, ignores difficult terrain from non-magical foliage;  jaws, Damage 2d12 piercing plus 2d6 poison;  claw (agile), Damage 3d10 slashing;  tail (reach 10 feet), Damage 3d10 bludgeoning;  horns (reach 10 feet), Damage 3d8 piercing; breath weapon 30-foot cone, 10d6 poison (Fortitude save instead of Reflex). * Red ignore concealed from smoke;  jaws, Damage 2d12 piercing plus 2d6 fire;  claw (agile), Damage 4d6 slashing;  tail (reach 10 feet), Damage 3d10 bludgeoning;  wing (reach 10 feet), Damage 3d8 bludgeoning; breath weapon 30-foot cone, 10d6 fire. * White climb Speed 25 feet on ice only;  jaws, Damage 3d6 piercing plus 2d6 cold;  claw (agile), Damage 3d10 slashing;  tail (reach 10 feet), Damage 3d10 bludgeoning; breath weapon 30Ã¢â,¬'foot cone, 10d6 cold. * Brass burrow Speed 20 feet;  jaws, Damage 3d8 piercing plus 2d4 fire;  claw (agile), 3d10 slashing;  tail (reach 10 feet), Damage 3d10 bludgeoning;  spikes (reach 10 feet), Damage 3d8 piercing; breath weapon 60-foot line, 15d4 fire. * Bronze swim Speed 40 feet;  jaws, Damage 2d10 piercing plus 1d12 electricity;  claw (agile), Damage 3d10 slashing;  tail (reach 10 feet), Damage 3d10 bludgeoning;  wing (reach 10 feet), Damage 3d8 slashing; breath weapon 80-foot line, 6d12 electricity. * Copper climb Speed 25 feet on stone only;  jaws, Damage 2d12 piercing plus 2d6 acid; Melee [one-action] claw (agile), Damage 3d10 slashing;  tail (reach 10 feet), Damage 3d10 bludgeoning;  wing (reach 10 feet), Damage 3d8 bludgeoning; breath weapon 60-foot line, 10d6 acid. * Gold swim Speed 40 feet;  jaws, Damage 2d12 piercing plus 2d6 fire;  claw (agile), Damage 4d6 slashing;  tail (reach 10 feet), Damage 3d10 bludgeoning;  horns (reach 10 feet), Damage 3d8 piercing; breath weapon 30-foot cone, 6d10 fire. * Silver walk on clouds;  jaws, Damage 2d12 piercing plus 2d6 cold;  claw (agile), Damage 3d10 slashing;  tail (reach 10), Damage 3d10 bludgeoning; breath weapon 30-foot cone, 8d8 cold.	DESC:&nl;Heightened (8th) Your battle form is Huge, you gain a +20Ã¢â,¬'foot status bonus to your fly Speed, and your attacks have 10-foot reach (or 15-foot reach if they previously had 10-foot reach). You instead gain AC = 21 + your level, 15 temporary HP, an attack modifier of +28, a damage bonus of +12, Athletics +28, and a +14 status bonus to breath weapon damage.	INFO:SpellLevel|6	INFO:Casting|somatic, verbal
