SHRINK ITEM				TYPE:Spell.Polymorph.Transmutation.Arcane.Primal							RANGE:touch																TARGETAREA:one nonmagical object up to 20 cubic feet in volume and up to 80 Bulk											DURATION:1 day									DESC:You shrink the target to roughly the size of a coin. This reduces it to negligible Bulk. You can Dismiss the spell, and the spell ends if you toss the object onto a solid surface. The object can't be used to attack or cause damage during the process of it returning to normal size. If there isn't room for the object to return to normal size when the spell ends, the spell's duration continues until the object is in a location large enough to accommodate its normal size.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												INFO:SpellLevel|3	INFO:Casting|10 minutes (somatic, verbal)
SIGIL					TYPE:Spell.Cantrip.Transmutation.Arcane.Divine.Occult.Primal					RANGE:touch																TARGETAREA:one creature or object																			DURATION:unlimited (see below)						DESC:You harmlessly place your unique magical sigil, which is about 1 square inch in size, on the targeted creature or object. The mark can be visible or invisible, and you can change it from one state to another by using an Interact action to touch the target. The mark can be scrubbed or scraped off with 5 minutes of work. If it's on a creature, it fades naturally over the course of a week. The time before the mark fades increases depending on your heightened level.	DESC:&nl;Heightened (3rd) The sigil instead fades after 1 month.	DESC:&nl;Heightened (5th) The sigil instead fades after 1 year.	DESC:&nl;Heightened (7th) The sigil never fades.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														INFO:SpellLevel|Cantrip	INFO:Casting|somatic, verbal
SILENCE				TYPE:Spell.Illusion.Divine.Occult										RANGE:touch																TARGETAREA:one willing creature																			DURATION:1 minute									DESC:The target makes no sound, preventing creatures from noticing it using hearing or other senses alone. The target can't use sonic attacks, nor can it use actions with the auditory trait. This prevents it from casting spells that include verbal components.	DESC:&nl;Heightened (4th) The spell effect emanates from the touched creature, silencing all sound in or passing through a 10- foot radius and preventing any auditory and sonic effects in the affected area. While within the radius, creatures are subject to the same effects as the target. Depending upon the position of the effect, a creature might notice the lack of sound reaching it (blocking off the noise coming from a party, for example).																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					INFO:SpellLevel|2	INFO:Casting|material, somatic
SLEEP					TYPE:Spell.Enchantment.Incapacitation.Mental.Sleep.Arcane.Occult					RANGE:30 feet; Area 5-foot burst																																															DESC:Each creature in the area becomes drowsy and might fall asleep. A creature that falls unconscious from this spell doesn't fall prone or release what it's holding. This spell doesn't prevent creatures from waking up due to a successful Perception check, limiting its utility in combat.	DESC:&nl;Critical Success The creature is unaffected.	DESC:&nl;Success The creature takes a Ã¢â,¬"1 status penalty to Perception checks for 1 round.	DESC:&nl;Failure The creature falls unconscious. If it's still unconscious after 1 minute, it wakes up automatically.	DESC:&nl;Critical Failure The creature falls unconscious. If it's still unconscious after 1 hour, it wakes up automatically.	DESC:&nl;Heightened (4th) The creatures fall unconscious for 1 round on a failure or 1 minute on a critical failure. They fall prone and release what they're holding, and they can't attempt Perception checks to wake up. When the duration ends, the creature is sleeping normally instead of automatically waking up.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				INFO:SpellLevel|1	INFO:Casting|somatic, verbal
SLOW					TYPE:Spell.Transmutation.Arcane.Occult.Primal								RANGE:30 feet															TARGETAREA:one creature																					DURATION:1 minute									DESC:You dilate the flow of time around the target, slowing its actions.	DESC:&nl;Critical Success The target is unaffected.	DESC:&nl;Success The target is slowed 1 for 1 round.	DESC:&nl;Failure The target is slowed 1 for 1 minute.	DESC:&nl;Critical Failure The target is slowed 2 for 1 minute.	DESC:&nl;Heightened (6th) You can target up to 10 creatures.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														INFO:SpellLevel|3	INFO:Casting|somatic, verbal
SOLID FOG				TYPE:Spell.Conjuration.Water.Arcane.Primal								RANGE:120 feet; Area 20-foot burst																																				DURATION:1 minute									DESC:You conjure a bank of fog so thick it impedes movement as well as sight. This functions as obscuring mist (page 355), except that the area is also difficult terrain. You can Dismiss the spell.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											INFO:SpellLevel|4	INFO:Casting|material, somatic, verbal
SOOTHE				TYPE:Spell.Emotion.Enchantment.Healing.Mental.Occult							RANGE:30 feet															TARGETAREA:one willing living creature																		DURATION:1 minute									DESC:You grace the target's mind, boosting its mental defenses and healing its wounds. The target regains 1d10+4 Hit Points when you Cast the Spell and gains a +2 status bonus to saves against mental effects for the duration.	DESC:&nl;Heightened (+1) The amount of healing increases by 1d10+4.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																										INFO:SpellLevel|1	INFO:Casting|somatic, verbal
SOOTHING BALLAD			TYPE:Focus.Uncommon.Bard.Divination.Fortune								RANGE:30 feet															TARGETAREA:you and up to nine allies																													DESC:You draw upon your muse to soothe your allies. Choose one of the following three effects: * The spell attempts to counteract fear effects on the targets. * The spell attempts to counteract effects imposing paralysis on the targets. * The spell restores 7d8 Hit Points to the targets.	DESC:&nl;Heightened (+1) When used to heal, soothing ballad restores 1d8 more Hit Points.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												INFO:FocusLevel|7	INFO:Casting|somatic, verbal
SOOTHING WORDS			TYPE:Focus.Uncommon.Cleric.Emotion.Enchantment.Mental.FamilyDomain				RANGE:30 feet															TARGETAREA:one ally																					DURATION:1 round									DESC:You attempt to calm the target by uttering soothing words in a calm and even tone. The target gains a +1 status bonus to Will saving throws. This bonus increases to +2 against emotion effects. In addition, when you Cast this Spell, you can attempt to counteract one emotion effect on the target.	DESC:&nl;Heightened (5th) The bonus to saves increases to +2, or +3 against emotion effects.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																									INFO:PowerLevel|1	INFO:Casting|verbal
