WIND WALK				TYPE:Spell.Air.Transmutation.Primal										RANGE:touch																TARGETAREA:you and up to five creatures touched																	DURATION:8 hours									DESC:When you cast this spell, each target transforms into a vaguely cloud-like form and is picked up by a wind moving in the direction of your choice. You can change the wind's direction by using a single action, which has the concentrate trait. The wind carries the targets at a Speed of 20 miles per hour, but if any of the targets make an attack, Cast a Spell, come under attack, or otherwise enter encounter mode, the spell ends for all targets just after they roll initiative, and they drift gently to the ground.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					INFO:SpellLevel|8	INFO:Casting|10 minutes (material, somatic, verbal)
WISH					TYPE:Spell.Divination.Arcane																																																															DESC:You state a wish, making your greatest desire come true. A wish spell can produce any one of the following effects. * Duplicate any arcane spell of 9th level or lower. * Duplicate any non-arcane spell of 7th level or lower. * Produce any effect whose power level is in line with the above effects. * Reverse certain effects that refer to the wish spell. The GM might allow you to try using wish to produce greater effects than these, but doing so might be dangerous or the spell might have only a partial effect.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					INFO:SpellLevel|10	INFO:Casting|material, somatic, verbal
WORD OF FREEDOM			TYPE:Focus.Uncommon.Cleric.Enchantment.Mental.FreedomDomain						RANGE:30 feet															TARGETAREA:one creature																					DURATION:1 round									DESC:You utter a liberating word of power that frees a creature. You suppress one of the following conditions of your choice: confused, frightened, grabbed, or paralyzed. The target isn't affected by the chosen condition, and if you suppress the grabbed condition, the target automatically breaks free from any grab affecting it when you Cast the Spell. If you don't remove the effect that provided the condition, the condition returns after the spell ends. For example, if a spell was making the target confused for 1 minute, word of freedom would let the target act normally for a round, but the confused condition would return afterward.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																	INFO:FocusLevel|4	INFO:Casting|verbal
WORD OF TRUTH			TYPE:Focus.Uncommon.Cleric.Divination.TruthDomain																																																DURATION:sustained up to 1 minute						DESC:You speak a statement you believe to be true and that is free of any attempt to deceive through twisting words, omission, and so on. The statement must be 25 words or fewer. A symbol of your deity glows above your head, and anyone who sees you and hears your statement knows that you believe it to be true. Each time you Sustain this Spell, you can repeat this effect.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													INFO:FocusLevel|1	INFO:Casting|verbal
YOU'RE MINE				TYPE:Focus.Uncommon.Sorcerer.Emotion.Enchantment.Incapacitation.Mental				RANGE:30 feet															TARGETAREA:one creature																					DURATION:1 round									DESC:You manipulate the target's emotions, potentially allowing you to control it for a brief instant. The target must attempt a Will save.	DESC:&nl;Critical Success The target is unaffected.	DESC:&nl;Success The target is stunned 1.	DESC:&nl;Failure On the target's next turn, it's stunned 1 and you partially control it, causing it to take a single action of your choice. If it has actions left, it can act normally.	DESC:&nl;Critical Failure The target is controlled for 1 round.	DESC:&nl;Heightened (7th) On a failure, the target is controlled for 1 round. On a critical failure, the target is controlled for up to 1 minute; it receives a new Will save at the end of each of its turns, and on a success, the spell ends.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																	INFO:FocusLevel|5	INFO:Casting|somatic, verbal	INFO:SavingThrow|Will
ZEALOUS CONVICTION		TYPE:Spell.Enchantment.Divine.Occult									RANGE:30 feet															TARGETAREA:up to 10 willing creatures																		DURATION:10 minutes								DESC:You bypass your targets' rational minds, instilling them with unshakable conviction and zeal. The targets each gain 12 temporary Hit Points and a +2 status bonus to Will saves against mental effects, as their faith overrides the signals from their own bodies and minds. If you tell a target to do something, it must comply with your request, though if it would normally find the task repugnant, it can attempt a Will save at the end of its turn each round due to the cognitive dissonance. On a success, it ends the spell's effects on itself entirely.	DESC:&nl;Heightened (9th) The temporary Hit Points increase to 18, and the status bonus to Will saves increases to +3.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											INFO:SpellLevel|6	INFO:Casting|somatic, verbal
